text: The Egypt Hockey Federation (EHF) is the governing body of field hockey in Egypt. The Headquarters of EHF are in Nasr City, Cairo. It is affiliated to IHF International Hockey Federation and AHF African Hockey Federation. ==History== ==See also== *Egypt men's national field hockey team *African Hockey Federation ==References== ==External links== * FIH-Egypt * EHF-FB Egypt Hockey
